1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
What if your brain has a secret way to detox?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:09,200
Enter the glymphatic system, your brain's cleaning crew that works while you sleep.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:13,600
This network of vessels removes waste like amyloid-beta, linked to Alzheimer’s.

4
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:17,600
Recent studies show sleep quality directly impacts this system's efficiency.

5
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:20,400
So, better sleep means a healthier brain.

6
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:22,400
Are you getting enough rest?

7
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:26,800
Dive deeper into brain health—like and follow for more science insights!
